metadata.name: My Friend Frank #1
metadata.description: Frank lost his father Bart Stein and began to live a lonely life.  Like many others he was bullied for his apperance and called Frankenstein.  Running into the woods due to bullying he thought he would be alone forever.  He came upon a young boy who was also bullied.  Here is their story.  Full story and roadmap to be released.  You will not want to miss this one.
